#

Chunky Tomato Guacamole

10 min
$5
220 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Snack

Tags:

SnackAppetizer

Description

A fresh and zesty guacamole with a chunky twist, perfect for dipping or as a topping!

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • medium tomatoes: 2
  • red onion: 1/4
  • fresh cilantro: 2 tablespoons
  • lime: 1
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
